        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": "To Rotate the view, click and hold the left mouse button in the window. Move the mouse up or down, or left or right. In this mode the Rotation when moving the mouse left to right the object is being rotated about the local Y Axis passing through the Object."
        },
        {
