        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": "The axis for the up and down movement of the mouse is the Floor (0 Elevation). The axis of the left to right movement is the center of the Room. If you notice, with the Grid option on in Floor Plan view, there are 2 darker blue lines. One line that is horizontal and one that is vertical. Where these lines cross is the center of the Room and the intersection of the 2 lines is the pivot point of the left to right motion with the mouse."
